name: Run
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Our goal is to make Solana as developer-friendly as Ethereum. With our simple 4 step process, users will be able to launch projects in moments. Not only that, but scaling projects will be as simple as the click of a button. We aim to build a BETTER Infura for Solana.
